OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782850701
OL,3,CPoots defiant as calls grow for him to
OL,4,Cstep aside over Donaldson claims
OL,6,FStormont Speaker Edwin Poots has said
OL,7,Fhe "would never have protected Jeffrey
OL,8,FDonaldson in any circumstance".
OL,10,FMr Poots has faced calls to step aside
OL,11,Ffrom his role over his handling of an
OL,12,Fincident where a woman raised concern
OL,13,Fabout behaviour by Donaldson, the
OL,14,Fformer DUP leader.
OL,16,FMr Poots told the Assembly on Tuesday:
OL,17,F"If anybody has any notion that I done
OL,18,Fanything to protect Jeffrey Donaldson,
OL,19,Fafter all that he had done to me
OL,20,Fpreviously, they are living in some
OL,21,Fother world or other planet.
OL,26,@oD@DOUpD@^O]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782850701
OL,3,CPoots defiant as calls grow for him to
OL,4,Cstep aside over Donaldson claims
OL,6,F"I will be cleared of any of the
OL,7,Faccusations that have been made
OL,8,Fagainst me, by any individuals in this
OL,9,Fplace or outside of it.
OL,11,F"Because I have done nothing wrong, I
OL,12,Fmake that absolutely clear.
OL,14,F"I would never have protected Jeffrey
OL,15,FDonaldson in any circumstance had he
OL,16,Fdone wrong, but given what he done on
OL,17,Fme in particular previous to that, I
OL,18,Fdefinitely wouldn't have."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOUzD@ZO]
