OL,3,CPoots defiant as calls grow for him to
OL,4,Cstep aside over Donaldson claims
OL,6,FMr Poots has faced pressure from
OL,7,FStormont parties over his role in an
OL,8,Fincident where a woman raised concern
OL,9,Fabout behaviour by Donaldson.
OL,11,FEarlier, Sinn Fein had called on Mr
OL,12,FPoots to stand aside pending a DUP
OL,13,Finvestigation into claims of
OL,14,Finappropriate behaviour by Jeffrey
OL,15,FDonaldson.
OL,17,FSinn Fein Chief Whip Sinead Ennis told
OL,18,FMLAs that the incident raised "serious
OL,19,Fquestions" over his role as Speaker.
OL,26,@sD@PrryD@GrryD@YrrzD@_OU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
