OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782850701
OL,3,CPoots defiant as calls grow for him to
OL,4,Cstep aside over Donaldson claims
OL,6,FFormer DUP leader Donaldson was last
OL,7,Fweek convicted of 18 sex offences,
OL,8,Fincluding one count of rape, relating
OL,9,Fto abuse of two women when they were
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FSubsequent media reports have raised
OL,13,Fquestions about how much was known
OL,14,Fwithin the DUP about Donaldson's wider
OL,15,Fconduct in the period prior to his
OL,16,F2024 arrest over sex abuse allegations.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782850701
OL,3,CPoots defiant as calls grow for him to
OL,4,Cstep aside over Donaldson claims
OL,6,FQuestions have also been raised around
OL,7,Fwhether there was an awareness that
OL,8,FDonaldson was allegedly engaged in
OL,9,Fbehaviour in his private life that,
OL,10,Falthough legal, was at odds with
OL,11,Fpositions he adopted publicly.
OL,13,FThe DUP is commissioning an
OL,14,Findependent review into issues raised
OL,15,Fsince Donaldson was convicted.
OL,17,FMs Ennis raised the issue during a
OL,18,Fsitting of the Northern Ireland
OL,19,FAssembly on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
