PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782850701
OL,3,CPoots defiant as calls grow for him to
OL,4,Cstep aside over Donaldson claims
OL,6,FShe said: "Revelations over recent
OL,7,Fdays that members of the DUP,
OL,8,Fincluding the Assembly Speaker Edwin
OL,9,FPoots, had knowledge of the
OL,10,Fexploitation of a young woman by the
OL,11,Fnow convicted paedophile Jeffrey
OL,12,FDonaldson raises serious questions for
OL,13,Fthe DUP.
OL,26,@nD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782850701
OL,3,CPoots defiant as calls grow for him to
OL,4,Cstep aside over Donaldson claims
OL,6,F"Even if we accept that there were no
OL,7,Fcriminal or safeguarding issues, and
OL,8,Fthat remains to be seen; there was
OL,9,Fclearly knowledge of inappropriate
OL,10,Fbehaviour by Donaldson, which,
OL,11,Faccording to the current DUP leader
OL,12,F(Gavin Robinson), was not passed to
OL,13,Fthe party officers.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,413,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782850701
OL,3,CPoots defiant as calls grow for him to
OL,4,Cstep aside over Donaldson claims
OL,6,F"The result of this is that these
OL,7,Fissues were not raised or dealt with,
OL,8,Feven as the DUP elevated Donaldson to
OL,9,Fthe leadership of the DUP, effectively
OL,10,FDonaldson's behaviour was ignored, and
OL,11,Fin terms of this Assembly, it raises
OL,12,Fserious questions for Edwin Poots as
OL,13,FAssembly Speaker.
OL,15,F"This is at best a gross misjudgment
OL,16,Fby the Speaker, at worst it is a
OL,17,Ffundamental and disastrous moral
OL,18,Ffailure."
OL,20,FMs Ennis told MLAs that a "dangerous
OL,21,Fpaedophile went unchallenged".
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOUzD@IO]|D@[OU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
