PN,41209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782850701
OL,3,CPoots defiant as calls grow for him to
OL,4,Cstep aside over Donaldson claims
OL,6,FShe added: "Worse still, and despite
OL,7,Fclear and knowing red flags, he was
OL,8,Felected leader of the DUP.
OL,10,F"On that basis, I am calling for the
OL,11,Fspeaker to now stand aside pending the
OL,12,Ffull disclosure of all of the issues
OL,13,Fand any and all knowledge of them
OL,14,Fwithin the DUP about inappropriate
OL,15,Fbehaviour before and during
OL,16,FDonaldson's time as DUP leader."
OL,26,@nD@LOUrD@AOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
