OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782850701
OL,3,CPoots defiant as calls grow for him to
OL,4,Cstep aside over Donaldson claims
OL,6,FOn Monday, current DUP leader Gavin
OL,7,FRobinson said "it is clear" there are
OL,8,Fformer and current DUP members who had
OL,9,Finformation about the conduct of
OL,10,FDonaldson which was not shared with
OL,11,Fthe party.
OL,13,FSpeaking to the Assembly on Monday, Mr
OL,14,FPoots said there was "nothing of a
OL,15,Fcriminal or safeguarding nature
OL,16,Fraised" in the concerns of the woman.
OL,18,FHe said he had asked the chief
OL,19,Fexecutive of the Assembly to carry out
OL,20,Fan investigation relating to
OL,21,FDonaldson's actions when he was an MLA.
OL,26,@oD@OOUoD@[O]vD@VOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
