PN,41211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1782850701
OL,3,CPoots defiant as calls grow for him to
OL,4,Cstep aside over Donaldson claims
OL,6,FAsked if the investigation would also
OL,7,Flook at his own actions, Mr Poots
OL,8,Fsaid: "I don't have anything to answer
OL,9,Ffor because I did not engage in any
OL,10,Fmisbehaviour of any kind.
OL,12,F"This is an investigation which would
OL,13,Fallow potential victims of abuse by
OL,14,FJeffrey Donaldson to come forward."
OL,16,FHe added: "Let's be very clear about
OL,17,Fthis, this is about the paedophile
OL,18,FJeffrey Donaldson, nothing else."
OL,26,@pD@GOUtD@AOUvD@cO]xD@KOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
