OL,3,CPoots defiant as calls grow for him to
OL,4,Cstep aside over Donaldson claims
OL,6,FMr Poots said that "recusing myself is
OL,7,Fnot something that is necessary at
OL,8,Fthis point, because there is nothing
OL,9,Fto answer for".
